---
import { cities } from '../i18n/cities';
const popular = cities.slice(0, 6);
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko-KR" dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다 | 여기여</title>
    <meta name="description" content="요청하신 페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다. 여기여 홈페이지나 지역별 페이지를 이용해 주세요." />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://여기여.site/404/" />
    <style>
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      body { background: #030712; color: #f9fafb; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 2rem; }
      .container { text-align: center; max-width: 640px; width: 100%; }
      .code { font-size: 6rem; font-weight: 800; color: #2563eb; line-height: 1; }
      h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 1rem; color: #f9fafb; }
      p { color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; }
      .actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 2rem; }
      .btn-primary { background: #2563eb; color: #fff; padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem; border-radius: 0.75rem; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: background 0.2s; }
      .btn-primary:hover { background: #3b82f6; }
      .btn-secondary { background: #1f2937; color: #f9fafb; padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem; border-radius: 0.75rem; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; border: 1px solid #374151; transition: background 0.2s; }
      .btn-secondary:hover { background: #374151; }
      .cities { margin-top: 3rem; }
      .cities h2 { font-size: 0.875rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: #6b7280; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
      .city-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 0.5rem; }
      .city-link { background: #111827; border: 1px solid #1f2937; border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 0.75rem; text-decoration: none; color: #d1d5db; font-size: 0.85rem; transition: all 0.2s; }
      .city-link:hover { border-color: #2563eb; color: #93c5fd; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="code">404</div>
      <h1>페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다</h1>
      <p>요청하신 주소가 존재하지 않거나 이동되었습니다.<br />여기여 홈이나 지역별 페이지에서 최신 주소를 확인해보세요.</p>

      <div class="actions">
        <a href="/" class="btn-primary">🏠 여기여 홈으로</a>
        <a href="https://www.ygy01.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-secondary">여기여 바로가기 ↗</a>
      </div>

      <div class="cities">
        <h2>인기 지역 여기여</h2>
        <div class="city-grid">
          {popular.map((c) => (
            <a href={`/${c.slug}/`} class="city-link">{c.name} 여기여</a>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
